<h1 class="page-title">
    About this Information Finder
</h1>

<p>This tool shares information on what’s needed to apply for or renew a certification. This tool is only for information purposes—it is not part of the formal application or renewal process for certification.</p>

<h2>
    This finder is for...
</h2>

<ul>
    <li>People wanting information to become certified seafarers.</li>
    <li>Existing seafarers wanting information to renew their certification.</li>
</ul>

<p>A seafarer is someone who works on a commercial marine vessel.</p>

<h2>
    This finder isn’t for...
</h2>

<p>
    People who are pleasure craft operators (you’ll want to see
    <a href="https://www.tc.gc.ca/eng/marinesafety/debs-obs-paperwork-paperwork_operator-360.htm">National Pleasure Craft Operator Competency Program</a>).
</p>

